<SUBJECTS>ELECTION PRESIDENTIELLE,1995,PARTI DE DROITE,CANDIDAT ELECTORAL;INSTANCE</SUBJECTS>
<NAMES>GISCARD D'ESTAING VALERY,CHIRAC JACQUES,BALLADUR EDOUARD,MILLON CHARLES,LONGUET GERARD,LEOTARD FRANCOIS,BARRE RAYMOND,MONORY RENE,CHARETTE HERVE DE,UDF,PR,CDS</NAMES>
